<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Đơn đăng ký Seller chưa được duyệt</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f2f6f8;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px 12px;
            background-color: #f2f6f8;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }

        .header {
            background: #dc2626;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 28px 24px;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .note-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 16px 24px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>DON DANG KY SELLER CHUA DUOC DUYET</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Xin chao <%= username %>
                </h2>
                <p>Chung toi da xem xet don dang ky tro thanh Seller cua ban voi ten shop <strong>
                        <%= shopName %>
                    </strong>.</p>
                <p>Rat tiec, don cua ban hien chua duoc phe duyet tai thoi diem nay.</p>

                <div class="note-box">
                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #991b1b;"><strong>Ly do:</strong>
                        <%= adminNote %>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <p>Ban co the dieu chinh thong tin va gui lai don dang ky sau khi da cap nhat day du thong tin theo yeu
                    cau.</p>
                <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 13px;">Neu ban can ho tro them, vui long lien he voi doi ngu cham
                    soc khach hang cua chung toi.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ebay. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>Email nay duoc gui tu dong, vui long khong tra loi.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>